AddCardToHand, AddCardToOtherHand, AddMessage, AddMessages, AddPlayer, ChooseColor, ChooseObjective, ChooseStarterSide, CreateGame, DrawCard, GetGamesResponse, JoinGameRequest, JoinGameResponse, PlayCardRequest, PlayCardResponse, PromptColorChoice, PromptError, PromptObjectiveChoice, PromptStarterChoice, RemoveCardFromHand, RemoveCardFromOtherHand, SendChatMessage, SendPrivateChatMessage, SetColor, SetCommonCards, SetCommonObjectives, SetDeckTopType, SetGamePoints, SetGameState, SetHand, SetObjectivePoints, SetOtherHand, SetPersonalObjective, SetPlayArea, SetPlayers, SetStartOrder, SetWinners, SignalDeadlock, SignalDisconnection, SignalGameDeletion, SignalGameSuspension, Turn
public abstract class Payload extends Object
Generic abstract class for a message payload. All subclasses of this class are possible payloads for TCP messages. All payloads are immutable bean-like objects that can be serialized and deserialized to and from JSON.
